  "title": "*URGENT* Locum Pharmacy Technician - $20/hr (Central/East) #HRY",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Role Details</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Contract Duration: 6 months</p></li><li><p>Working Arrangement: Flexible (4 / 5 / 5.5 days per week)</p></li><li><p>Working Hours:</p><ul><li><p>Weekdays: 8.00am–5.00pm / 8.30am–5.30pm</p></li><li><p>Saturdays (alternate): 8.00am–12.00pm / 8.30am–12.30pm</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Work Location: Islandwide (multiple clinics)</p></li><li><p>Remuneration: $20/hr (no CPF contribution)</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Process prescriptions and dispense medications according to prescribed instructions</p></li><li><p>Support Medication Delivery Service (MDS) and PILBOX services</p></li><li><p>Provide tele-dispensing services where applicable</p></li><li><p>Assist in video consultations and medication reconciliation</p></li><li><p>Support pharmacy operations across different clinic locations as required</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>GCE ‘O’ Level with Certificate in Pharmacy Technician Course (MOH / PSS or equivalent) <strong>OR</strong></p></li><li><p>Diploma in Pharmaceutical Science</p></li><li><p>Comfortable travelling between multiple clinic locations</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Additional Information</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Pre-employment medical and vaccination check is required</p></li><li><p>Medical clearance takes approximately one week</p></li><li><p>Medical and vaccination costs will be covered upon commencement of work</p></li></ul><p><strong>Interested applicants, please email your updated CV to </strong><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">rachel.lim@recruitexpress.com.sg</a><strong> or WA 97527630 for more information.</strong></p><p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>EA Personnel No: R23116144<br />EA Personnel Name: Lim Ruo Yi, Rachel<br />Company EA License No.: Recruit Express Pte Ltd (99C4599)</p>",
